Package tage.audio.joal

package tage.audio.joal
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    tage.audio
    Wrapper for the audio package JOAL.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    JOALAudioEar
    This class extends the AudioEar abstract class and uses the JOAL Java interface to OpenAL (http://jogamp.org) to provide a JOAL-based audio ear.
    JOALAudioManager
    This class extends the AudioManager abstract class and uses the JOAL Java interface to OpenAL (http://jogamp.org) to provide a JOAL-based audio manager.
    JOALAudioPlayer
    This class extends the AudioPlayer abstract class and uses the JOAL Java interface to OpenAL (http://jogamp.org) to provide a JOAL-based audio player.
    JOALAudioResource
    This class represents an OpenAL (via JOAL) audio resource.
